                                                                                                                                    that process informaon that will be maintained in a Privacy Act system of records;

                                                                                                              PT-06a.[02]           new and signiﬁcantly modiﬁed system of records noces are submied to the OMB
                                                                                                                                    and appropriate congressional commiees for advance review for systems that
                                                                                                                                    process informaon that will be maintained in a Privacy Act system of records;

                                                                                                              PT-06b.               system of records noces are published in the Federal Register for systems that
                                                                                                                                    process informaon that will be maintained in a Privacy Act system of records;

                                                                                                              PT-06c.               system of records noces are kept accurate, up-to-date, and scoped in accordance
                                                                                                                                    with policy for systems that process informaon that will be maintained in a Privacy
                                                                                                                                    Act system of records.

